@startuml Sequence_Candidate_Applications
title Ứng Viên - Quản Lý Đơn Ứng Tuyển (Module D)

actor Candidate as "👤 Ứng viên"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant ApplicationService as "Application\nService"
participant JobService as "Job\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Nộp Đơn Ứng Tuyển ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Nộp đơn" (trên job detail)
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show application form
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Chọn CV & viết cover letter
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Validate (CV selected, cover letter optional)
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: POST /api/applications\n(tinTuyenDungId, hoSoCvId, thuNgo)
ApplicationService -> ApplicationService: Check if already applied
ApplicationService -> ApplicationService: Check duplicate (DuplicateApplicationException)
ApplicationService -> Database: Create don_ung_tuyen (status=MOI)
Database --> ApplicationService: Return applicationId
ApplicationService -> Database: Create lich_su_trang_thai (MOI)
Database --> ApplicationService: OK
ApplicationService -> JobService: Get job info (for notification)
JobService -> Database: Get tin_tuyen_dung
Database --> JobService: Job info
JobService --> ApplicationService: Job details
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Application submitted
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Nộp đơn thành công

== Danh Sách Đơn Ứng Tuyển ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Đơn của tôi"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: GET /api/applications?page=0&size=20
ApplicationService -> Database: Query don_ung_tuyen (candidateId)
Database --> ApplicationService: Return list
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Applications list
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị danh sách đơn

== Xem Chi Tiết Đơn ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click vào 1 đơn
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: GET /api/applications/{applicationId}
ApplicationService -> Database: Get don_ung_tuyen details
Database --> ApplicationService: Application details
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Full application info
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị chi tiết đơn\n(Job title, company, cover letter)

== Xem Lịch Sử Trạng Thái ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Lịch sử trạng thái"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: GET /api/applications/{applicationId}/history
ApplicationService -> Database: Query lich_su_trang_thai
Database --> ApplicationService: Status history
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Timeline data
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Hiển thị timeline\nMOI → REVIEW → PHONG_VAN → OFFER

== Xem CV Snapshot ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Xem CV đã nộp"
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: GET /api/applications/{applicationId}/cv-snapshot
ApplicationService -> Database: Get banSaoCvUrl
Database --> ApplicationService: CV URL
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: PDF URL
FrontEnd --> Candidate: Open PDF preview

== Hủy Đơn ==

Candidate -> FrontEnd: Click "Hủy đơn"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Confirm dialog
Candidate -> FrontEnd: Xác nhận hủy
FrontEnd -> ApplicationService: DELETE /api/applications/{applicationId}
ApplicationService -> Database: Delete don_ung_tuyen
Database --> ApplicationService: OK
ApplicationService --> FrontEnd: Application cancelled
FrontEnd --> Candidate: ✅ Hủy đơn thành công

@enduml
